'''Karl Andersson''' is a [[Sweden|Swedish]] [[canoe racing|sprint canoeist]] who competed in the early 1950s. He won a [[gold medal]] in the K-4 10000 m event at the [[1950 ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships]] in [[Copenhagen]].

